hopobject.body: What's the exchange rate for euros? supplementnaturals.com Years in Ring: 1985-1991, 1995-2005Years Behind Bars: 1992-1995, 1999 (among other arrests)Ever since being arrested for purse snatching as a 12-year-old, Tyson's been no stranger to law enforcement. Most notably, the ferocious former heavyweight champ was sentenced to 10 years in prison in 1992 (although he served only three) after being convicted of one count of rape and two counts of deviate sexual conduct. He added another noteworthy stint in prison to his record in 1999 after assualting two motorists after a 1998 traffic accident.
